								<h1>Tegrity Common Fixes</h1>
								
								<h3>Test my Computer</h3>
								<ul>
								<li>
								<a href="http://supportu.tegrity.com/tegrityutils/Diagnostic.aspx">
								Tegrity Diagnostic</a></li>
								</ul>
								<h3>Recommended Browser Settings</h3>
								<ul>
								<li>
								<a href="documents/ie-settings.pdf">Internet Explorer Browser Settings</a></li>
								<li>
								<a href="documents/firefox-settings.pdf">Firefox Browser Settings</a></li>
								</ul>
								
								
								<h3>Common Windows Fixes</h3>
								<ul>
								<li>Install the latest 
								<a href="http://windows.microsoft.com/en-US/windows/downloads/windows-media-player">Windows Media Player</a>.</li>
								<li>Install the latest 
								<a href="http://www.microsoft.com/getsilverlight/Get-Started/Install/Default.aspx">Silverlight</a>.</li>
								<li>Firefox Users: Install the latest 
								<a href="http://www.interoperabilitybridges.com/windows-media-player-firefox-plugin-download">Windows Media Player plugin for Firefox</a>.</li>
								<li>Chrome Users: Install the latest 
								<a href="http://www.interoperabilitybridges.com/wmp-extension-for-chrome">Windows Media Player plugin for Chrome</a>.</li>
								</ul>
								
								<h3>Windows 8</h3>
								<p>Tegrity recordings can be played on Windows 8. Users have a choice of using Firefox or Google Chrome:</p>
								<ul>
								<li>Tegrity settings for 
								<a href="documents/tegrity-firefox-windows-8.pdf">Firefox</a></li>
								<li>Tegrity settings for 
								<a href="documents/Google%20Chrome%20on%20Windows%208.pdf">Chrome</a></li>
								</ul>
								
								<h3>Mac</h3>
								<ul>
								<li>Mac Tegrity Plugin <a href="documents/mac-teg-plugin.pdf">PDF</a></li>
								<li>Note: Tegrity only supports the Safari browser on Mac.</li>
								</ul>
								
								<h3>Other Possible Solutions:</h3>
								<ul>
								<li>Requirements for viewing a Tegrity recording: 
								<span lang="en-US">
								<font size="2" face="Calibri,sans-serif">
								<span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt">
								<a target="_blank" href="https://help.tegrity.com/what-are-the-requirements-for-a-viewing-a-tegrity-recording.html">
								https://help.tegrity.com/what-are-the-requirements-for-a-viewing-a-tegrity-recording.html</a></span></font></span></li>
								<li>Antivirus: <span>Temporarily disable your 
								Antivirus software, or add tegrity as an 
								exception to your antivirus.</span></li>
								<li>Communication: <span>Exit out of all 
								communication programs (i.e. Skype, Google Talk)</span></li>
								</ul>
								<p>&nbsp;</p>
								
